In two or three months I contemplate to commence an other journey. Could I receive his Excellencys sanction to an expedition through the interior of N.S.W. I do not doubt, that this journey will prove to be successful, whereas success in increasing the collections within the boundaries of this colony will be very quest[ion]able;


      editorial addition — obscured by binding.
 as I have been in all the main localities for plants during the last two summers. Not less than 2550 miles have been travelled by me from Nov to April last.
